{"type": "article", "id": 8002, "title": "自定义笔记本保护套", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-01T07:23:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052346053vKd1e9NupAcRIiz.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t来自旧金山的 Jolt Team 推出了一款自定义笔记本保护套，这款保护套被安装在电脑上之后，可以允许用户在其表面搭建乐高风格的积木图案。既可以保护电脑，又能够充分体现个性。不过，这个作品看起来是乐高风格，却不是仅仅和LEGO合作的，Mega Bloks, PixelBlocks, KRE-O 和 K’NEX Bricks 都在合作范围内，为消费者提供了更多的选择。目前这款产品正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/joltteam/brik-case\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234603TgCUEfG1HpMzcdKr.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234603bZmjLQ5JhpTG1Uz3.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052346045XBy8L0wA1O7Gket.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234604WsDklcORJAFgN9bp.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.62571429\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}